{"id": 1027, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都曾怎样努力地维护自己的仪表形象？", "description": "虽然不是天生丽质，但我也不能放弃自己。（题图来自：Roman Muradov）", "record_count": 5025, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130139WyF1zox5fGXvtgLQ.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-03T11:06:50Z", "options": [{"id": 84480, "content": "只要有能有镜子一样效果的东西，都要照一下！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632293}, {"id": 84481, "content": "不在路上吃东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189764}, {"id": 84482, "content": "放屁先塞住自己的耳朵", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535094}, {"id": 84483, "content": "出门会穿衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456251}, {"id": 84995, "content": "每天洗澡  出门前检查装扮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617465}, {"id": 84740, "content": "努力的不发脾气.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634402}, {"id": 84485, "content": "夏天出门前洗澡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256207}, {"id": 84997, "content": "变白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172786}, {"id": 84486, "content": "坐在电脑前敷面膜，死也要美美哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631999}, {"id": 84487, "content": "我假装自己是个很有修养的人，装了三十多年了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217407}, {"id": 84488, "content": "晚上洗好头发早上起来全束起来，没辙又起来重洗。来不及了就到水龙头底下洗个刘海", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633590}, {"id": 86024, "content": "梳头梳大半个钟头", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630726}, {"id": 84489, "content": "坚持洗头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579627}, {"id": 84490, "content": "多看一些穿衣打扮的介绍，让自己变得会穿衣服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616465}, {"id": 85002, "content": "再生气不说脏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635129}, {"id": 84491, "content": "拍个照的到时候要先捋一捋刘海。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633600}, {"id": 82700, "content": "午睡时小心翼翼，生怕压坏发型", "image": null, "praise_count": 231, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84492, "content": "拍照的时候要先捋捋刘海。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633600}, {"id": 82701, "content": "新鞋被人踩了一道印子，找没人的地方悄悄擦拭", "image": null, "praise_count": 318, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84493, "content": "不提塑料袋", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540792}, {"id": 84749, "content": "装作有人在暗地里看着我然后各种保持形象", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634432}, {"id": 85005, "content": "永恒 减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523464}, {"id": 82702, "content": "为新纹身穿了一夏天无袖，晒成人型背心", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84494, "content": "开车与头枕保持一定空隙，就怕头发压下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115094}, {"id": 84750, "content": "衣着整洁干净不夸张，影响他人心情的个人小细节问题不当人面做，总之不引人注目就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634431}, {"id": 85006, "content": "头可断血可流发型不能乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583432}, {"id": 82703, "content": "风大的时候歪头走路，使风向和刘海的偏向保持一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 501, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84495, "content": "出门前洗头，挺直腰板，保持微笑，走路的时候脑中自带bgm，对路过的美女行注目礼，内心一直自我催眠：我最有魅力?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517073}, {"id": 82704, "content": "停不下来地拉抻西服，不允许出现一点褶皱", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 84496, "content": "每天都坚持用阳光沐浴自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633618}, {"id": 84497, "content": "人前文質彬彬，斯文有禮，人後釋放自己，粗言穢語~~???", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551008}, {"id": 84498, "content": "公共场所吃东西蜜汁尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633228}, {"id": 84754, "content": "对女生绅士", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451587}, {"id": 89106, "content": "不躲避路人视线 昂首挺胸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646515}, {"id": 85011, "content": "360度无死角照镜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584921}, {"id": 85523, "content": "不化妆但会用口红", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469783}, {"id": 84500, "content": "宁可迟到，也要洗头……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398183}, {"id": 85012, "content": "360度无死角照镜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584921}, {"id": 84501, "content": "奇思妙想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633544}, {"id": 84757, "content": "穿得体的衣服，提升气质", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634493}, {"id": 84502, "content": "只要是出门，总是要美美的^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633166}, {"id": 85782, "content": "不想洗脸的时候在家里带着不出去", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633447}, {"id": 84503, "content": "出门前花很久时间考虑服饰搭配", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633635}, {"id": 84504, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450371}, {"id": 85016, "content": "坐地铁会往玻璃门上瞧，是不是头发乱了眼镜歪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635170}, {"id": 88856, "content": "多看好书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645149}, {"id": 94232, "content": "口红", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663214}, {"id": 84505, "content": "把背挺得笔直的  直到腰痛肩膀僵硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633667}, {"id": 84506, "content": "点头 微笑 少说话 将头发自然的苟到耳后", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633677}, {"id": 84507, "content": "做自己，", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633679}]}